        "content": "<p>I was working on adding a warning when an stream used for new user announcements, new stream announcements is being archived. There are two issues <a href=\"https://github.com/zulip/zulip/pull/25685\">#25685</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/zulip/zulip/pull/22110\">#22110</a> regarding this both proposing different solutions. I am not sure which solution is more appropriate. I have added screenshots below based on approaches suggested in both the issues.  </p>\n<p>Based on solution in <a href=\"https://github.com/zulip/zulip/pull/25685\">#25685</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/dc/tts9Rc7hUHqYV2IlrDHo42P5/Screenshot-from-2023-06-30-20-59-01.png\">Screenshot-from-2023-06-30-20-59-01.png</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/3a/2YmdL22eijAfupub3mQ3mdFO/Screenshot-from-2023-06-30-20-55-57.png\">Screenshot-from-2023-06-30-20-55-57.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/dc/tts9Rc7hUHqYV2IlrDHo42P5/Screenshot-from-2023-06-30-20-59-01.png\" title=\"Screenshot-from-2023-06-30-20-59-01.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/dc/tts9Rc7hUHqYV2IlrDHo42P5/Screenshot-from-2023-06-30-20-59-01.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/3a/2YmdL22eijAfupub3mQ3mdFO/Screenshot-from-2023-06-30-20-55-57.png\" title=\"Screenshot-from-2023-06-30-20-55-57.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/3a/2YmdL22eijAfupub3mQ3mdFO/Screenshot-from-2023-06-30-20-55-57.png\"></a></div>",
